profile: At Steam Dry Canada, our customers are our business. Whether it is our carpet, upholstery, area rug, furnace and duct cleaning, indoor air quality division or the flood rescue division, we strive to give our customers superior, detailed and precise results. Our service technicians will provide these superior services with integrity and sincere customer service. We don't send salespeople into our customers homes, we send qualified technicians that are focused on meeting and exceeding our customers expectations. We want to give our customers the most enjoyable in-home service that they have ever received and we are not satisfied until our customers are satisfied, guaranteed.

profile:
The first thing to know about us: We are not perfect. We are a professional team of 20 humans technicians and always try to reach perfection. 
****What differentiates us from others: if we make a mistake, you call and we fix it.    

1Clean Air is a residential and commercial company that services air ducts and carpet cleaning, upholstery, dryer vent, air conditioning unit cleaning and 24-hour emergency water damage restorations. We promise you quality and offer you state-of-the-art cleaning equipment and 24/7 responsive time to your doorstep. We have offices in Ottawa and in Gatineau and we service the surrounding areas such as Nepean, Gloucester, Kanata, Orleans, South Keys, Barrhaven & Stittsville. 

Why 1Clean Air? 
•	Superior equipment 
•	Highly trained technicians with cleaning certification
•	We have an A+ rated with the Better Business Bureau (BBB)
•	We have thousands of satisfied customers
